Tell me the 2nd maximum num in the array.

No bubblesort!
No quicksort!
No heapsort!

At first, get the largest num in the array, delete this num.
At last, scan the array again annd get the 2nd maxinum num in the array.

or

// 时间复杂度O(n)
const int MINNUMBER = -32767;
int Find2ndMax(int Array[], int count)
{
    int MaxNumber = Array[0];
    int SecMax = MINNUMBER;
    for(int i = 1; i < count; i++){
        if(Array[i] > MaxNumber){
            SecMax = MaxNumber;
            MaxNumber = Array[i];
        }
        else
        {
            if(Array[i] > SecMax){
                SecMax = Array[i];
            }
        }
    }
    return SecMaxx;
}
